# Cloud Run Hello Service

This is my first Google Cloud Run project.

## Overview

This project deploys a small Python web service using Flask on **Google Cloud Run**.  
It responds with a simple greeting message.

## Features

- Containerized Python app
- Deployed on Cloud Run
- Auto-scaling managed by Google
- Public URL for access
- Logging via Cloud Logging

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repo  
2. Deploy to Cloud Run via GCP Console  
3. Allow unauthenticated access

